# Equalize

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:image, "~> 0.38"},
  {:kino, "~> 0.13"}
])
```

## Prepare image

```elixir
dark_image = Image.open!("/home/livebook/vix/dark.jpg")
```

## Execution

```elixir
[
  dark_image,
  Image.equalize!(dark_image),
  Image.equalize!(dark_image, :each),
  Image.equalize!(dark_image, :luminance)
]
|> Kino.Layout.grid(columns: 2)
```
